      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but it's a bit too vague. I need it to be more specific about the \"radicalism\" part. Can you add some sections that explicitly call out things like gender ideology in schools or the breakdown of the nuclear family? We need to frame it so the audience understands that these progressive policies aren't just different opinions, but are actually dangerous threats to the future of our country. Make it sound like a fight for survival.",
